<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4684691>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Munidopsis macphersoni sp. nov., female holotype, cl 7.8 mm, pcl 5.2 mm, (MNHN IU-2010-1429). (A) cephalothorax and abdomen, dorsal; (B) carapace, right lateral view; (C) right antenna and antennule, ventral view; (D) right basal antennular article, lateral view; (E) right maxilliped 3; (F) right crista dentata; (G) right cheliped dorsal view; (H) right cheliped carpus and ischiomerus, lateral view; (I) right ischiomerus, mesial view; (J) left cheliped fingers, ventral view; (K) right pereopod 2, dorsal view; (L) right pereopod 3, dorsal view; (M) telson; (N) sternal plastron. Scale: A, B, G–L = 1.0 mm; C–F, M, N = 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4684691/files/figure.png" .
